high_descs: Turn to your right, then go forward and turn right to face the sink.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the egg.
Take the knife to the sink.
Wash the knife in the sink and remove it from the sink.
Turn around to your left and go to the coffee maker, then turn left again so that the coffee maker is on your right.
Open the drawer on your right, near the end of the counter, put the knife in the drawer and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife away in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around to the right and locate the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Keep the knife, and turn to the right just a bit by the sink.
Put the knife in the sink and turn the water on. Turn the water off and pick up the knife.
Take the knife and turn around the counter directly behind.
Open the left top drawer and put the knife inside. Shut the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Clean a knife to put it away.

high_descs: Turn left, then turn left again to go to the sink.
Pick up the knife, to the left of the egg.
Go to the sink basin to your right.
Wash the knife in the sink.
Turn around and go to the counter, near the toaster.
Put the knife in the drawer that is under the bowl.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife in a drawer.
